trans-unit.source: Defines a set of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID"></xref> fields that each correspond to a command function provided by the host environment.
trans-unit.target: Define um conjunto de <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID"> </xref> campos que cada correspondem a uma função de comando fornecida pelo ambiente anfitrião.

trans-unit.source: MenuCommands contains a set of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> fields that can be used to specify a command to link when adding a command using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A> method of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService>.
trans-unit.target: MenuCommands contém um conjunto de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>campos que podem ser utilizados para especificar um comando para ligar ao adicionar um comando utilizando o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A>método de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>
